take a model_name
pick all attributes of the model if existing, exit otherways
for each attribute save an hash containing the name of the attribute and its type
if the index view action of the model exists open the file, exit otherways 
open the index view action for the model and add:
 - the form 
 - the pagination partial call
place the pagination partial inside the shared view directory


the form will be inserted before the line containing
- table_for

the form will be in the form:


- form_for @search do |f|
  - f.fields_for @search.conditions do |families|
    = families.label :daddy_contains, t(:daddy)
    = families.text_field :daddy_contains, :size => 12
    = families.label :mommy_contains, t(:mommy)
    = families.text_field :mommy_contains, :size => 12
    = families.label :body, t(:body) 
    = families.text_field :body_contains, :size => 20
    = families.label :wedding_after, t(:wedding_after)   
    = families.date_select :wedding_after
  = f.submit "Search"

